      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、今のところ\nもう一回お願いします！！",
      "startTime": 12.9306575139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、今度はどうでしょうか\nステップにミスはなかったと……思います",
      "startTime": 20.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか……はい\nもう一度、お願いします！",
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……ミスがないだけではダメ\nお客さんに情熱が伝わらないと……",
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（東京に来てから沙季のパフォーマンスは良くなってる）\n（ここで、もうひと皮むけることが出来れば……）",
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
